paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the interaction of amiodarone with the hERG channel, encoded by the KCNH2 gene, using mutagenesis and in silico docking. No specific genetic variants in KCNH2 with clinical significance or penetrance data were reported.

challenges: The paper focused on functional studies and did not report specific genetic variants with clinical data.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper primarily discusses the functional interaction of amiodarone with the hERG channel and does not provide specific genetic variant data in the KCNH2 gene.
